OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has no
OL,7,Fcredible plan to fund the armed forces
OL,8,Fthe government wants, leaving the UK
OL,9,Fincreasingly reliant on its allies,
OL,10,FMPs have warned.
OL,12,FThe gap between the MoD's budget and
OL,13,Fthe cost of the has ballooned to #16.9
OL,14,Fbillion, its largest deficit ever,
OL,15,Fdespite an injection of #46.3 billion
OL,16,Fover the next 10 years.
