OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,FBut the influential Public Accounts
OL,7,FCommittee (PAC) has warned that the
OL,8,Freal deficit could be closer to #29
OL,9,Fbillion as some parts of the armed
OL,10,Fforces only included capabilities that
OL,11,Fwere affordable rather than all those
OL,12,Fthe government had requested.
OL,14,FDame Meg Hillier, chairwoman of the
OL,15,Fcross-party PAC, said the Ministry's
OL,16,F"lack of a credible plan... leaves us
OL,17,Fin an alarming place" in an
OL,18,Fincreasingly volatile world.
