OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,FLabour said the report was "more
OL,7,Fproof" that the Conservatives had
OL,8,Ffailed to "deal with the deep problems
OL,9,Fin the MoD".
OL,11,FIn a report on the MoD's Equipment
OL,12,FPlan published on Friday, the PAC
OL,13,Fwarned that gaps in military
OL,14,Fcapabilities had left the UK more
OL,15,Freliant on its allies to protect its
OL,16,Fown interests, while the credibility
OL,17,Fof Britain's armed forces had been
OL,18,F"undermined".
