OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe MPs pointed to recruitment issues,
OL,7,Fwith more people leaving the armed
OL,8,Fforces than being recruited, and the
OL,9,Fmothballing of Royal Navy vessels due
OL,10,Fto crew shortages.
OL,12,FIn January, ministers had to deny
OL,13,Freports that would be mothballed ahead
OL,14,Fof their planned retirement dates in
OL,15,Fthe mid-2030s due to a lack of
OL,16,Favailable crew.
OL,18,FThe MPs said the UK's armed forces
OL,19,F"continue to fulfil a crucial
OL,20,Finternational role".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
