OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,F"However, many of its allies are
OL,7,Ffacing similar challenges to the UK,
OL,8,Fwhich might affect their ability and
OL,9,Fwillingness to continue providing
OL,10,Fextensive support," they added.
OL,12,FThe PAC urged the government to
OL,13,Fdevelop plans to mitigate the impact
OL,14,Fon the UK of the risk that allied
OL,15,Fsupport might be curtailed or
OL,16,Fwithdrawn.
OL,18,FMPs also renewed their criticism of
OL,19,Fthe MoD's procurement processes,
OL,20,Fsaying that slow had caused gaps in
OL,21,Fmilitary capability.
