OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,FOnly two of the MoD's 46 equipment
OL,7,Fprogrammes are currently rated as
OL,8,Fhighly likely to be delivered to time,
OL,9,Fbudget and quality, while successful
OL,10,Fdelivery seems unachievable for five
OL,11,Fprojects including nuclear submarine
OL,12,Freactors, new communications
OL,13,Ftechnology and missiles.
OL,15,FThe report accused the MoD of dodging
OL,16,F"major decisions" about cancelling
OL,17,Fprocurement programmes it cannot
OL,18,Fafford, relying too much on an
OL,19,Fassumption that defence spending will
OL,20,Frise to 2.5%, in line with the
OL,21,Fgovernment's long-term ambition.
