OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FIt also highlighted that the decision
OL,12,Fto prioritise the Defence Nuclear
OL,13,FEnterprise, which manages the , had
OL,14,Fincreased the deficit and risked
OL,15,Ffurther squeezing budgets for
OL,16,Fconventional forces.
OL,18,FDame Meg said the problem is not a new
OL,19,Fone, and that the situation seems to
OL,20,Fbe getting worse.
