OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,F"Year-on-year our committee has seen
OL,7,Fbudget overruns and delays in defence
OL,8,Fprocurement. A lack of discipline in
OL,9,Fthe MoD's budgeting and approach has
OL,10,Fled to an inconsistent plan that just
OL,11,Fisn't a reliable overview of the
OL,12,Fequipment programme's affordability,"
OL,13,Fshe said.
OL,15,F"We're disappointed that not only are
OL,16,Fthe same problems we're used to seeing
OL,17,Fon display here, but they also appear
OL,18,Fto be getting worse. Despite a budget
OL,19,Fincrease, this year's plan shows a
OL,20,Fclear deterioration in affordability.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/10
