OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,F"The MoD must get to a better grip, or
OL,7,Fit won't be able to deliver the
OL,8,Fmilitary capabilities our country
OL,9,Fneeds."
OL,11,FJohn Healey, Labour's shadow defence
OL,12,Fsecretary, said Conservative ministers
OL,13,F"might talk a good game on defence"
OL,14,Fbut that the report is "more proof of
OL,15,Ftheir failure" to deal with the deep
OL,16,Fproblems in the MoD.
