OL,3,CMoD lacks 'credible plan' to fund UK's
OL,4,Carmed forces, MPs warn
OL,6,F"Ministers have lost control of the
OL,7,Fdefence budget, failed to fix the
OL,8,F'broken' defence procurement system
OL,9,Fand wasted billions of pounds of
OL,10,Fpublic money," he added.
OL,12,F"With war in the Europe and conflict
OL,13,Fin the Middle East, ministers risk
OL,14,Fleaving our armed forces without the
OL,15,Fequipment they need to fight and
OL,16,Ffulfil our Nato obligations."
